data.description: Let's dive into this awesome 3-bed, 3-bath ranch-style Home w/the bonus of a Finished Basement! Main Floor living areas offer amazing space w/a surprisingly large Family Rm w/vaulted ceiling & a bumped out Breakfast Rm.   Kitchen boast a center island & is ready for your touches! Brand new LVP through the entire Main Floor along w/Fresh Paint.  Cozy wood fireplace is perfect for upcoming winter nights. Another surprise is the ensuite Front Bedroom! Perfect for guests or an office! Primary Bdrm also has vaulted ceilings & walk in closet. Addt Bdrm & hall Full BA round out the main floor. The finished basement is a bonus hangout place. Plus a generous storage room! It's got all the space you need. 2 Car garage on a great cul-de-sac lot. New roof in 2017 and New HVAC in 2020
